:name: NRF52840
:description: This script runs the NRF52840DK and flashs a given image

using sysbus

mach create
machine LoadPlatformDescription @$RENODE_CPU_BIN_REPL

emulation CreateServerSocketTerminal 3456 "term" False
connector Connect sysbus.uart0 term

macro reset
"""
    sysbus LoadELF $image_file
"""
runMacro $reset